---
title: "_getAssetOutAmount (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_bound_time: elapsedTime = min(elapsedTime, auctionDuration)
    q_bound_time --> q_compute_multiplier: compute priceMultiplier

    q_compute_multiplier --> q_get_out_price: priceMultiplier = starting - (starting - ending) * elapsed / duration
    q_get_out_price --> q_compute_usd: assetOutUsdPrice = _getAssetPrice(s_assetOut, withValidation)

    q_compute_usd --> q_step1: step1 = mulDivUp(amountIn, assetInUsdPrice, 10^decimals)
    q_step1 --> q_step2: step2 = mulWadUp(step1, priceMultiplier)
    q_step2 --> q_step3: step3 = mulDivUp(step2, 10^assetOutDecimals, assetOutUsdPrice)
    q_step3 --> [*]: return assetOutAmount (step3)

    note right of q_compute_multiplier
        INV-001: priceMultiplier is bounded between endingPriceMultiplier and startingPriceMultiplier
        INV-002: All rounding operations use ceiling (mulDivUp, mulWadUp) in protocol favor
        INV-003: assetOutAmount >= 1 for all valid inputs (amountIn > 0, prices > 0, decimals > 0)
        INV-004: Linear decay curve P = Pmax - (Pmax - Pmin) * t / duration
    end note
